4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, requiring no prior knowledge. Over a span of 16 weeks, students attend three classes weekly with a maximum of 12 participants per class. Participants will learn Python, SQL, Streamlit, and various machine learning algorithms, while focusing on real-life case challenges. The course culminates in a recognized certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. The program includes expert instructors with extensive backgrounds in artificial intelligence and machine learning. For further details and to enroll, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop